org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures

Class DerivedFeatures

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseQueryGroup
      • org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseGeneratedPatternGroup
        • org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures.DerivedFeatures
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQueryGroup

    public final class DerivedFeatures
extends BaseGeneratedPatternGroup
    A pattern group formed of all public patterns defined in DerivedFeatures.vql.

    Use the static instance as any org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IPatternGroup, to conveniently prepare a VIATRA Query engine for matching all patterns originally defined in file DerivedFeatures.vql, in order to achieve better performance than one-by-one on-demand matcher initialization.

    From package org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures, the group contains the definition of the following patterns:

    • actionInput
    • actionOutput
    • activityGroup
    • activityGroupInActivity
    • activityNode
    • activityNodeActivity
    • activityEdgeInGroup
